{"service_name": "INFOSEC Audit services", "service_id": "5903805656858624", "company_name": "Selex ES Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Selex ES Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     INFOSEC Audit services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    INFOSEC Audit services to audit activities, projects, programmes and implementations to all aspects of prevailing HMG INFOSEC policy. Security Policy Framework (SPF), ISO27001 or client selected criteria are used; audits are executed according to ISO19011 and can be used to gain assurance for onward reporting and effective operational security management.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Fully trained audit staff for Type 1 or 2 audits\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Lead Auditor qualified supported by CLAS if required for HMG\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     INFOSEC, ISO27001:2013 is at the focus of our audit activities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Extensive HMG experience - use of SPF as audit datum\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supports certification or compliance claims to ISO27001\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Pre-certification health checks to support certification audit\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Client fully engaged, plans and ToRs agreed prior to audit\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Audit Report fully discussed with client (no surprise approach)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Validation of treatment approach with the client, effective countermeasures\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Complementary services available eg penetration test, accreditation, protective monitoring\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     All audits undertaken by fully trained audit staff\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Full Terms of Reference, plans and audit reports provided\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Proactive engagement to support treatment plans and treatment approaches\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     All products discussed with client to ensure appropriate messaging\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     All evidence included in audit report to support independent review\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3583 to \u00a31326 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/5903805656858624-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/5903805656858624-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/5903805656858624-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        <